john friedrich was caught outside a gasoline station near perth 
the capital of western australia state after driving 1850 miles 
across the continent in a used station wagon purchased for 11750 
in cash 
police said friedrich who had shaved off his distinctive beard 
offered no resistance there was no word about the missing millions 
