the hopes of polish society 
a part of the divergencies remained but there is nothing 
strange in that differences exist and they will appear in the 
future such is the nature of society 
however the feeling of joint responsibility for the course of 
events should lead to moderating them the essence is to create 
effective instruments to overcome discrepancies not keeping them 
secret or remaining silent about them 
the round table was the first extremely significant step toward 
this this is why the dialogue can turn out to be a priceless 
element in the accomplishments of our work 
