mob boss nicodemo little nicky scarfo 
and seven associates were convicted wednesday on firstdegree 
murder charges in the 1985 slaying of another gangster and could 
face the electric chair 
jurors deliberated about three hours before returning the 
verdict on all counts in the slaying of frank frankie flowers 
dalfonso in july 1985 
