electronics to be paid 10000 in exchange for trying to obtain the 
contract at the same time parkin said teledyne agreed that he 
would be paid 150000 if he was successful 
if he was not successful then there would be no fee paid 
savaides said 
when he learned of parkins arrangement with teledyne savaides 
said my reaction was pure amazement and shocki didnt 
believe teledyne would enter into an agreement like this 
savaides testified that after parkin reached the deal with 
